title: Delicate White Flowers
description: A close-up image of a cluster of small, delicate white flowers with five petals each. The flowers have a hint of green in the center and are set against a rocky background, highlighting their natural habitat.

title: Wildlife Habitat
description: An illustrated scene depicting a diverse wildlife habitat. In the foreground, a group of flamingos stands in a shallow body of water surrounded by lush green grass. In the background, various animals such as deer can be seen grazing near trees. The sky is filled with birds in flight. Two circular insets feature close-up images of a bird of prey and a wild cat, highlighting the diversity of species in this ecosystem.

title: Lone Tree in Rocky Landscape
description: A tall, majestic tree stands alone on a rocky slope, with a clear blue sky in the background. The tree has a thick trunk and lush green foliage, contrasting with the rugged, rocky terrain beside it.

title: Mountain Goat in Motion
description: A mountain goat is captured mid-leap, showcasing its agility as it bounds across a grassy landscape. The background features rocky terrain and patches of green vegetation, highlighting the natural habitat of the animal.
